Top-pair production at the LHC through NNLO QCD and NLO EW
Authors: Czakon, Heymes, Mitov, Pagani, Tsinikos, Zaro (2017)
Contact: mczakon@physik.rwth-aachen.de
         dheymes@hep.phy.cam.ac.uk
         andrewp@hep.phy.cam.ac.uk
	 davide.pagani@tum.de
	 ioannis.tsinikos@tum.be
	 marco.zaro@lpthe.jussieu.fr

When using these results please cite arXiv:1705.04105.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Top-quark mass mtop : 172.5 GeV
Higgs-boson mass : 125.09 GeV
W-boson mass : 80.385 GeV
Z-boson mass : 91.1876 GeV
EW renormalisation : Gmu-scheme
Gmu = 1.1663787Â·10^{-5} GeV^{-2}

Mtt      : Invariant mass distribution of the top-quark pair
PTtt      : Transverse momentum distribution of the top-quark pair
dytt	: difference of the absolute values of rapidities of top and antitop quarks i.e. |y(t)|-|y(tx)|
Ytt   : Rapidity distribution of the top-quark pair
Yt   : Rapidity distribution of the top quark
Ytx   : Rapidity distribution of the antitop quark pair
Yavt  : Averaged rapidity distribution of the top-quark rapidity distribution and the antitop-quark rapidity distribution       
PTavt    : Averaged transverse momentum distribution of the top-quark transverse momentum distribution and the antitop-quark transverse momentum distribution 
PTt     : Top-quark transverse momentum distribution
PTtx     : Antitop-quark transverse momentum distribution


Central scales: 	mu0 = HT/4 for Mtt, PTtt, Ytt, Yavt, Yt, Ytx, dytt  (arXiv: 1606.03350)
                       	mu0 = MT/2 for PTavt           	(arXiv: 1606.03350)
			mu0 = MTt/2 for PTt 		(MTt = sqrt(mtop^2 + PTt^2))
			mu0 = MTtx/2 for PTtx         	(MTtx = sqrt(mtop^2 + PTtx^2))
			

PDF-sets:
LUXQED17 : "LUXqed17_plus_PDF4LHC15_nnlo_100"
NNPDF31: "NNPDF31_nnlo_as_0118_luxqed"


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

( {a,b} := {muR=a*mu0,muF=b*mu0}, K := (QCDxEW)/QCD and total-*=scale-* plus pdf-* added in quadrature  )
Files with the name "*-pheno.dat" contain the following 10 columns:
                 bin-center  central-value scale-min scale-max pdf-min pdf-max total-min total-max bin-width K
Units:
PTavt,Mtt:	[GeV]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [GeV]  [1]
Ytt,Yavt,Yt,Ytx,dytt: [1]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [pb]  [1]  [1]

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Files with the name "*-LUXQED17-all_members.dat" contain the following 116 columns ( with {a,b} := {muR=a*mu0,muF=b*mu0} ):
                 bin-center  {1,1}  {1/2,1/2}  {2,2}  {1/2,1}  {1,1/2}  {2,1} {1,2} {PDFmembers : 1-107} bin-width

Files with the name "*-NNPDF31-all_members.dat" contain the following 109 columns ( with {a,b} := {muR=a*mu0,muF=b*mu0} ):
                 bin-center  {1,1}  {1/2,1/2}  {2,2}  {1/2,1}  {1,1/2}  {2,1} {1,2} {PDFmembers : 1-100} bin-width

Units:
PTavt,Mtt:	[GeV] [pb] ... [pb]  [GeV]
Ytt,Yavt,Yt,Ytx,dytt:	[1]   [pb] ... [pb]  [1]

